                        {
                            "type": "options.text",
                            "id": "fc833bb5-b15c-4eed-a8c1-b91cd72ba61f",
                            "text": "Look at the Portrait",
                            "nodes": [
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.showCloseUp",
                                    "imageName": "Kartoffleman_Portrait.png"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "6b1b2481-1891-47c1-977d-a9b380db9c26",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": null,
                                    "text": "Interesting! It says, \"Kartofflemann was born as a the son of a humble potato farmer, but after inadvertently becoming a local hero of the Battle Against the Great Mole, or \"Gro√üe Maulwurfsschlacht\" as it's known, he rose to prominence as the Lord of his local region of Fad Kartoffle Ort.\"",
                                    "emotion": "1",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "67343dbc-8d6c-4e54-9080-07f97aef2068",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": null,
                                    "text": "There's more: \"While not the sharpest pencil in the box, nor the strongest... erm... pencil in the box... Kartofflemann's unflappable spirit and blindingly ignorant courage made him a hero of his day.\"",
                                    "emotion": "4",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "0d6cb0de-c205-47dd-89db-0319121ef7da",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": null,
                                    "text": "I love how the engraver put the \"erm...\" right on the plaque, as if he was making up the inscription as he went along!",
                                    "emotion": "1",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "afc39f7c-47df-4faf-88f3-331cd3df6115",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": null,
                                    "text": "This makes it sound like he's no longer alive, but I hope he is. I have a great mole on my back that I'd like removed.",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.hideCloseUp",
                                    "waitForSeconds": 1
                                }
                            ],
